Significantly restructured code; implemented all 3 functions

Made progress towards VCF output. Need to restructure to handle cases when one VCF position has SNVs and indels

More progress towards AmpliPy variants and consensus
Added additional header line to output SAM for AmpliPy Trim

Added example for primer trim at start

Seem to have finished trimming implementation
Seemingly added quality trim for reverse reads
Seem to have fixed reverse primer trim
Refactored CIGAR fixing into own function
Moved trim_read functions to non-nested so they can be used in both Trim and AIO modes
Some progress towards trimming (need to understand how the primer trimming algo works
Refactored to make it easier to compute index on-the-fly if we need to
Added fast algorithm for finding overlapping primers
AmpliPy Index also outputs primer indices
